item.title: CVE-2023-26112|2023-04-03T05:00:01.443Z -- n%2Fa -- configobj
item.description: All versions of the package configobj are vulnerable to Regular Expression Denial of Service (ReDoS) via the validate function, using (.+?)\((.*)\). **Note:** This is only exploitable in the case of a developer, putting the offending value in a server side configuration file.
